    "We use LoRA (Hu et al., 2022; Mangrulkar et al., 2022) to carry out the pretraining in this resourceconstrained setting.",
    "The LoRA adapters are applied to all the linear modules in the model.",
    "These include {k_proj, q_proj, v_proj, and o_proj} modules from self attention layers along with {gate_proj, up_proj, and down_proj} modules from MLP layers.",
    "We use a consistent LoRA configuration of a rank value of 32 and an alpha value of 64 for fair comparison.",
    "Training Hyperparameters."
